      <title>特里谢表示美联储可能会在欧洲央行之后首次降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-15/trichet-says-first-fed-rate-cut-may-come-after-ecb-s-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行前行长特里谢表示，美国顽固的潜在通胀可能意味着欧元区将先降息。特里谢于周三上午在《彭博市场：欧洲收盘》中向阿利克斯·斯蒂尔和盖伊·约翰逊表示。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-15/trichet-says-first-fed-rate-cut-may-come-after-ecb-s-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 14:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>10 年期收益率将在 1 小时内重新测试 2023 年高点和低点：BMO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-15/10-year-yield-to-retest-2023-highs-and-lows-in-1h-bmo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BMO 全球资产管理公司固定收益和货币市场主管 Earl Davis 表示，2023 年将成为 2024 年债券收益率信息丰富的一年。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-15/10-year-yield-to-retest-2023-highs-and-lows-in-1h-bmo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 14:12:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储威廉姆斯表示谈论三月份降息“为时过早”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/fed-s-williams-says-talk-of-march-rate-cut-is-premature</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约联邦储备银行行长约翰·威廉姆斯表示，官员们现在开始考虑最早在3月份降息还为时过早，因为他们正在考虑政策的限制性是否足以让通胀率回到2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/fed-s-williams-says-talk-of-march-rate-cut-is-premature</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 13:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构敦促中国企业增加股息和回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/regulator-urges-chinese-companies-to-boost-dividends-buybacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国证券监管机构要求上市公司提高股息以奖励投资者，并表示将加强对不支付股息的公司的监管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/regulator-urges-chinese-companies-to-boost-dividends-buybacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 13:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区不断上升的衰退风险未能促使欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/euro-zone-s-rising-recession-chances-fail-to-shift-ecb-on-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着私营部门活动恶化，欧元区陷入衰退的可能性上升——强化了欧洲央行迄今为止抵制的降息理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/euro-zone-s-rising-recession-chances-fail-to-shift-ecb-on-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 10:32:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
