    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市创四月以来最长单周上涨势头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/european-stocks-set-for-fifth-week-of-gains-on-rate-cut-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市将迎来自 4 月份以来最长的每周上涨趋势，乐观情绪是央行准备开始降息，推动斯托克 600 指数交投于 2022 年初以来的最高水平附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-15/european-stocks-set-for-fifth-week-of-gains-on-rate-cut-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 08:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
